title: I think it's duplicate
body: I've been using dove for some time now. This particular product seems to be duplicate. Because the soap lacks the characteristic velvety feel. The aroma is not the same as the original dove soap. It doesn't lather much. Not moisturizing as well. I have seen a few reviews claiming for it to be a duplicate product. But since there are many positive reviews, i ignored the negative ones. Also I got a good deal on its price. But this is not the orginal dove. I am never buying from this seller again. Disappointed
